revised_title: Proceedings of the Royal Society of London - November 15, 1883
tldr: This article presents a list of transactions and publications from November 15, 1883, including a factor table for the sixth million by James Glaisher, F.R.S., which contains the least factor of every number not divisible by 2, 3, or 5 between 5,000,000 and 6,000,000.
